HEADWORD: Fluter
<hw>Flut"er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One who
plays on the flute; a flutist or flautist.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One who makes grooves or flutings.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

